long_description:
In case you haven’t heard, our historic Stanford Court Hotel in Nob Hill recently got a facelift of sorts. We’re calling it a reboot. While moving into the future with tech-forward and eco-friendly amenities, we also recognize the rich history and maverick spirit that has made San Francisco what it is today.

Our multi-million dollar reboot has scattered new, exciting features around the hotel, from our new music room, revisioned lobby, new restaurant and bar, and more. In this installation highlighting SCH reboot, we want to focus on our completely renovated rooms.

The rebooted rooms at Stanford Court Hotel now feature sleek, minimalist decor with custom-designed furniture. Power down after exploring a city dedicated to powering-up. Stark whites and grays emboldened by rich hues of blue and yellow help to pedal-down an active day around San Francisco.

A lush, Simmons pillow-top mattress in every room goes well with our “Nod Hill” sleep program, made to ensure that guests enjoy a good night’s sleep. Our Nod Hill sleep program offers a selection of hypoallergenic or feather pillows to fit guest preference. Additionally, Jambox speakers are available for use so guests can listen to relaxing tunes or white noise to lull them to sleep. Ear plugs and down comforters help make way for a deep slumber that recharges guests for the next day.

Our tech-forward and eco-friendly amenities offer practical, in-room comfort. Brush up on the day’s events using PressReader on your tablet, smartphone, or laptop and gain unlimited access to local and international publications. In the mood to Netflix and chill? Each room is equipped with Google Chromecast so guests can access Netflix, Hulu, Google Play using the room’s  49” HD television.

Need something from the front desk? Simply text the concierge. 

 

If you’re looking to unplug, book a room featuring a premium view for sweeping skyline views from our hilltop haven.

At Stanford Court Hotel, we know how hard it is to leave your best friend behind. That’s why we’re dog friendly. For a $50 deep-cleaning fee, bring along your pup and receive pet-friendly goodies. We’ll supply poop bags, a lint roller, chew toys you can bring home with you, dog food, bowls, and a plush dog bed for use during your stay.

We also like to keep an eye on the small details, such as our towel warmers, mini fridge and reusable water bottles with refillable stations located in the lobby . Relax in comfort and help us decrease our carbon footprint in one of the most forward-thinking cities in the world.

Check out room options and special offers on our website. Receive special offers only available by booking direct with Stanford Court Hotel.

--

Stanford Court is a boutique hotel located in Nob Hill. Close to Chinatown, Union Square, and North Beach, Stanford Court Hotel offers free bike rentals to make every part of San Francisco accessible to our guests.
